рџЏҐ AI-First Healthcare CRM Platform

AI-First Healthcare CRM is a modern full-stack Customer Relationship Management (CRM) platform built for Medical Representatives to efficiently manage Healthcare Professionals (HCPs). The platform leverages Artificial Intelligence to automate doctor interaction summaries, generate professional follow-up emails, recommend next actions, prioritize interactions, and provide an intelligent CRM assistant for enhanced productivity.
