рџ”Ќ How It Works
Medical Representative logs a doctor interaction.
Interaction details are securely stored in PostgreSQL.
AI processes the interaction using LangGraph and Groq LLM.
AI generates:
Professional Interaction Summary
Follow-up Email
Recommended Next Action
Priority Level
Dashboard updates in real time.
AI CRM Assistant answers CRM-related queries using stored database information.

вљ™пёЏ Installation
Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/AI-CRM-PROJ.git

Navigate to the project directory

cd AI-CRM-PROJ
Backend Setup
cd backend

python -m venv venv

venv\Scripts\activate

pip install -r requirements.txt

uvicorn app.main:app --reload
Frontend Setup
cd ../frontend

npm install

npm run dev

Open in your browser

http://localhost:5173

рџ”‘ Environment Variables

Create a .env file inside the backend folder.

DATABASE_URL=your_postgresql_connection_string

GROQ_API_KEY=your_groq_api_key

