рџ“Њ Note

This project uses Render's Free Tier for backend hosting.

The backend automatically enters sleep mode after inactivity. The first AI request may take 30вЂ“60 seconds while the service wakes up. During this time, the chatbot displays a loading indicator informing users that the AI service is connecting.
